Author: livipup
Text: I did get back to a healthy weight for maybe a month or two and it didn't happen at all in that time. I don't know my exact weight at the moment, but I feel like I've probably lost a lot just by checking out places like my hands, wrists, and chest. It only started happening again yesterday.
